precis:
Regulations Amending the MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 which deal with
matters such as cross-border fishing, catch and possession limits in the
sport fishery, rough fish, the deadline for removing ice-fishing huts in
the spring, and to add or remove certain bodies of water from the lists
of waters to which specific conservation measures apply.
